    <head><placeName key="CN0140211T03AA">魏恒州報德寺</placeName><persName key="A003024">釋道登</persName>傳七</head><p><anchor n="T.50.2060.0471c15"/><lb ed="T" n="0471c15"/><persName key="A003024">釋道登</persName>。姓<ptr target="fn16"/>苪<ptr target="fn17"/><placeName key="CN0371122Z03AA">東莞</placeName>人聰警異倫殊有信力。<lb ed="T" n="0471c16"/>聞<placeName key="CN0320303Z01AA">徐州</placeName>有<persName key="A015421">僧藥</persName>者雅明經論。挾策從之研<lb ed="T" n="0471c17"/>綜涅槃法花勝鬘。後從<persName key="A002253">僧淵</persName>學究成論。年<lb ed="T" n="0471c18"/>造知命譽動<placeName key="CN0140211Z09AA">魏都</placeName>。北土宗之。累信徵請。<persName key="A003024">登</persName><lb ed="T" n="0471c19"/>問同學<persName key="A005084">法度</persName>曰。此請可乎。<persName key="A005084">度</persName>曰。此國道學<lb ed="T" n="0471c20"/>如林師匠百數。何世無行藏。何時無通塞。<lb ed="T" n="0471c21"/>十方含靈皆應度脫。何容盡期。南國相勸行<lb ed="T" n="0471c22"/>矣。如<persName key="A001204">慧遠</persName>拂衣<placeName key="CN0360402M01AA">廬阜</placeName>。<persName key="A001800">曇諦</persName>絕迹<placeName key="CN0320583Z13AA">昆山</placeName>。<placeName key="CN0320303Z23AA">彭城</placeName><lb ed="T" n="0471c23"/><persName key="A002809">劉遺民</persName>辭事就閑。斯並自是一方。何必盡<lb ed="T" n="0471c24"/>命虛想巖穴遠追巢許。縱復如此終不離<lb ed="T" n="0471c25"/>小乘之機。豈欲使人在我先道不益世者<lb ed="T" n="0471c26"/>哉。隨方適化為物津梁不亦快乎。<persName key="A003024">登</persName>即受<lb ed="T" n="0471c27"/>請<persName key="A005084">度</persName>亦隨行。及到<placeName key="CN0410311A02AA">洛陽</placeName>君臣僧尼莫不賓<lb ed="T" n="0471c28"/>禮。魏主邀<persName key="A003024">登</persName>昆季策授榮爵。以其本姓不<lb ed="T" n="0471c29"/>華。改<ptr target="fn＊"/>苪為耐。講說之盛四時不輟。未趣<lb ed="T" n="0472a01"/><placeName key="CN0140225M01AA">恒岳</placeName>以息浮競。學侶追隨相仍山舍不免<lb ed="T" n="0472a02"/>談授。遂終于<placeName key="CN0140211T03AA">報德寺</placeName>焉。春秋八十有五。即<lb ed="T" n="0472a03"/><date from-iso="0500" key="j19037321905192" to-iso="0504">魏景明年</date>也。<ptr target="fn01"/></p>
